							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Give feedback on existing episodes
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="https://www.patreon.com/c/lemonadestand" class="gradient-button w-full px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 via-lime-500 to-green-500 text-white rounded-xl font-medium hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 inline-block text-center">
						Join Zest
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Juice Tier -->
				<div class="pricing-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
