					</div>
					<ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Everything in Zest tier
						</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
