						</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Extra book club episode monthly
						</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Participate in book discussions
						</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Suggest books for book club
						</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Year of Kindness video responses
						</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Movie club watch-alongs
						</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							<span class="mr-2">‚úì</span> Movie follow-up episodes
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="https://www.patreon.com/c/lemonadestand" class="gradient-button w-full px-6 py-3 border-2 border-lime-500 dark:border-lime-400 text-lime-500 dark:text-lime-400 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-lime-50 dark:hover:bg-lime-950 transition-colors inline-block text-center">
						Get Full Access
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- FAQ Section -->
			<div class="mt-24">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
					Frequently Asked <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-lime-500 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Questions</span>
				</h2>
				<div class="grid gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">What's included in the bonus episodes?</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Each bonus episode gives you a whole extra hour of fresh squeezed Lemonade Stand content weekly, including continued discussions, new topics, and comment responses!</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">How does the Book Club work?</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Each month we read a selected book together. You'll get an extra book club episode, can participate in the discussions, and even suggest future books for the club!</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">What is the Year of Kindness?</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Twice a month, one of our hosts will record video responses to particularly mean comments, turning negativity into a positive learning experience for everyone.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">How do movie watch-alongs work?</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Join us for synchronized watching of movies and documentaries, followed by dedicated episodes discussing the film with the community!</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>